    <h2>Cleveral</h2>
    <h3>CONDITION-BASED PREDICTIVE MAINTENANCE</h3>
    <p>Cleveral is a cloud  platform designed to collect Data  from structures through a system of sensors and, building on Machine Learning algorithms, schedule maintenance and predict damages.
Cleveral allows your company to be constantly aware of the condition of your structures, and perform maintenance only if an anomalous condition is detected, implying a significant cost reduction with respect to standard untargeted maintenance programs.</p>
